import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form'
import Label from 'react-bootstrap/FloatingLabel'
import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button'

const TaskTodo = () => {


  return (
    <Form>
      <Form.Group>
        <Label label="Titulo" className="mb-3">
          <Form.Control type="text"/>
        </Label>
        <Label label="Descripción" className="mb-3">
          <Form.Control as="textarea" rows={3} cols={60}/>
        </Label>
      </Form.Group >
      <Button variant="primary">Añadir tarea</Button>
    </Form>
  )
}

export default TaskTodo
